Remove debris, dead grass, loose the top layer

Pour grass seed and product into the canister,
connect the hose and turn on the water. and
fill with an appropriate amount of water, then
turn the water off for at least 30 seconds to
allow proper coating of the seeds. When you
are ready, turn the water back on and start
seeding the area you want to treat.

Water your newly seeded area 2-3 times a day,
keep the soil moist for the first 14 days.
